- Apply type based approach to
  - Vector Rotate
  - Vector Scale
  - Draw Polygon

- Use exception to display error help

- Incorperate type chechking at module connection time

Rotate:
  - input vector  : V | P   | [P]
  - control point : V | P   | [P]
  - angle         : N | [N] | [[N]]

Scale:
  - input vector  : V | P   | [P]
  - scaler        : N | V   | P   | [P]

